ops::bit::ShrAssign::shr_assign.doc:
Performs the `>>=` operation.

# Examples

```
let mut x: u8 = 5;
x >>= 1;
assert_eq!(x, 2);

let mut x: u8 = 2;
x >>= 1;
assert_eq!(x, 1);
```

